projectGridLines.title: Graviton - Monitoring
projectGridLines.description:
Title: Graviton - Monitoring


Description: You'll be responsible for converting client requirements given to you

by Finance SMEs into PRDs. Solutioning & coordinating with engineering, QA &

marketing teams to launch fully functional features is expected as part of the role.

An ability to empathize from the user's point of view will get you far in this role. An

understanding of equity & credit valuations is also preferred.

Skill sets: Excel, Figma, SQL

Traits expectation: Excellent communication skills. Prior leadership experience

mandatory via Position of Responsibility in clubs or own startups, etc. Students with

prior product management internships or at least product portfolios are also

strongly preferred. An understanding of equity & credit valuations is also expected.


Expected learning: Gain skills in cross-functional collaboration, user-centered

design, and equity/credit valuation understanding.

Specific courses required for project execution: Official Finance Minor not

necessary but these courses are mandatory: FOFA, DRM, BAV, SAPM with an

offshoot of 35/50.
